{"id":"9781","name":"Mastgur","tagline":"Media post to Mastodon for iOS via Imgur upload.","icon":"ios15 c4292093695 g59511","latest":"28920","description":"\n\t\t\t\t\t<p><img alt=\"image\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/43663476/127241975-4e26a587-1cea-49c3-a655-1a14138162a7.png\"></p>\n<h2>Media post to Mastodon for iOS via Imgur upload.</h2>\n<p>The ~~upcoming~~ now available! <a href=\"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/mastodon-for-iphone/id1571998974\"><strong>Mastodon for iOS app</strong></a> currently has a single Siri Shortcut action - \"Post [Text] on Mastodon\" - which only allows one to pass plain text to the app (and then to the service.) When a friend of mine <a href=\"https://mstdn.cloud.themaymeow.com/@emma/106654320972606699\">replied</a> to my links to <a href=\"https://github.com/extratone/i/issues/85\">my Share Sheet-destined Mastodon for iOS Siri Shortcut</a> requesting for clarification, I just sortof... whipped this one up without any revision or hesitation, and then felt compelled to publish it when it immediately functioned correctly on <a href=\"https://mastodon.social/@DavidBlue/106655155851383761\">its very first run</a>. (100% certain that success made it a first to do so among my various projects in Siri Shortcuts.)</p>\n<p>â‡¨ <a href=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/43663476/127242192-d55b5a1a-661f-44b8-8c46-746930bc132c.MOV\"><strong>Video Demo</strong></a></p>\n<h2>Steps</h2>\n<ol>\n<li>Prompts to select from Photos app (single file mode.)</li>\n<li>Prompts text input for the (optional) <code>Title</code> of the Imgur post.</li>\n<li>Prompts text input for the (optional) <code>Description</code> of the Imgur post - by default, I have also added #iOS and #social-media, but obviously, please personalize these for your own use.</li>\n<li>Uploads the media to Imgur <em>anonymously</em> (by Default) and retrieves the Direct URL to the corresponding post.</li>\n<li>Prompts text input in front of said retrieved URL for the actual content of the Toot.</li>\n<li>Posts &lt;your text&gt; &lt;imgur  url&gt; <a href=\"https://mastodon.social/@DavidBlue/106655409169365663\">to Mastodon</a>!</li>\n</ol>\n<h3>Mastodon Details</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>\"<a href=\"https://joinmastodon.org\">What's that?</a>\"</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://joinmastodon.org/apps\">joinmastodon.org/apps</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.patreon.com/mastodon\">The Mastodon Project's Patreon Page</a> (Become a patron to gain beta access to the iOS app, coming very soon!)</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://bilge.world/mastodon-ios-apps\">My celebration of the <em>third-party</em> Mastodon apps currently available on iOS</a></li>\n</ul>\n<hr>\n<h2>Contact</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://bit.ly/whoisdavidblue\"><strong>VCF Contact Card</strong></a></li>\n<li><a href=\"mailto:davidblue@extratone.com\">Email</a> </li>\n<li><a href=\"https://twitter.com/NeoYokel\">Twitter</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://mastodon.social/@DavidBlue\">Mastodon</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://discord.gg/0b9KQUKP858b0iZF\">Discord</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.notion.so/rotund/9fdc8e9610b34b8f991ebc148b760055?v=c170b58650c04fbdb7adc551a73d16a7\"><em>Everywhere</em></a>...</li>\n</ul>\n<p><img alt=\"Masto Mascot iOS Art\" src=\"https://i.snap.as/Y624NGHM.jpg\"></p>\n\t\t\t\t","releasenotes":"<p><strong>1.0 - July 28, 2021, 12:41 a.m.</strong></p>"}